% if: executable(fish)

Fish - Path Variables

Use the [prgm]set[/prgm] command in fish to create a path variable (colon-delimited).

# Create a path variable
$ [prgm]set[/prgm] [arg]--path[/arg] [arg-value]<NAME>[/arg-value] [arg-value]<VALUE>[/arg-value]

# Modify a path variable
$ [prgm]set[/prgm] [arg]--append[/arg] [arg-value]<NAME>[/arg-value] [arg-value]<VALUE>[/arg-value]
$ [prgm]set[/prgm] [arg]--prepend[/arg] [arg-value]<NAME>[/arg-value] [arg-value]<VALUE>[/arg-value]
